sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Model
    participant Hook as AlignDevicesHook
    participant Store as WeightsMap (CPU/Disk)
    participant GPU

    Note over User,GPU: Setup Phase (once)
    User->>Model: dispatch_model() / cpu_offload()
    Model->>Hook: attach_align_device_hook()
    Hook->>Model: init_hook() — move all params to "meta" device
    Note right of Model: Module params = meta tensors<br/>(zero VRAM used)
    Hook->>Store: weights_map holds real tensors<br/>(CPU dict / OffloadedWeightsLoader)

    Note over User,GPU: Inference — Forward Pass per Module
    User->>Model: model(input)
    Model->>Hook: pre_forward(module, input)
    loop For each parameter in module
        Hook->>Store: weights_map[param_name]
        Store-->>Hook: tensor (CPU RAM or disk read)
        Hook->>GPU: set_module_tensor_to_device(meta → cuda)
    end
    Hook->>GPU: send_to_device(input → cuda)

    Hook->>Model: call original forward()
    Model->>GPU: compute (all weights resident)
    GPU-->>Model: output tensor

    Model->>Hook: post_forward(module, output)
    loop For each parameter in module
        Hook->>GPU: set_module_tensor_to_device(cuda → meta)
        Note right of GPU: VRAM freed
    end
    Hook-->>User: output (moved to input device if io_same_device=True)

    Note over User,GPU: Repeat for every module in sequence